5b52b9f3157a959\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 876, "output": 1160, "cacheRead": 30720, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32756, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778218407375, "responseId": "resp_0c5681154ed6a8170169fd75a7fb8c819da0d89f4bd12c412c"}}
